ort to WooCommerce 2.6.2</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to ajax loading of product thumbnails</li>\n<li>New &#8211; Italian language</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.8 &#8211; Released: Apr 29, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.5.1</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.5.5</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to Flatsome</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCommerce Wishlist</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCommerce Frequently Bought Together</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCommerce Save for Later</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCoomerce Ajax Search</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to YITH WooCommerce Product Bundles</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; prevent badges from showing in WooCommerce emails</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.7 &#8211; Released: Jan 22, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.4.1</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.5</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; hidden badges in WooCommerce mini-cart</li>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; fixed minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.6 &#8211; Released: Dec 21, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; fixed minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.5 &#8211; Released: Dec 18, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WordPress 4.4</li>\n<li>New &#8211; support to WooCommerce 2.4.12</li>\n<li>New &#8211; possibility to show/hide badges in sidebars</li>\n<li>New &#8211; possibility to show/hide WooCommerce default &#8220;On Sale&#8221; badge when the product has another badge.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.3 &#8211; Released: Dec 01, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak &#8211; fixed minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.2 &#8211; Released: Nov 09, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Compatibility with more themes</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.2.1 &#8211; Released: Oct 28, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.9 &#8211; Released: Aug 21, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WordPress 4.3</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; removed badges in cart and checkout</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; minor bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.7 &#8211; Released: Aug 14, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommerce 2.4.4</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.6 &#8211; Released: Aug 12, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WordPress 4.2.4</li>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommerce 2.4.2</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; WPML deprecated functions</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.5 &#8211; Released: Jul 24, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; WPML Compatibility</li>\n<li>New &#8211; Compatibility with more themes</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Bug with widget sidebar on header</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.4 &#8211; Released: Jul 10, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommerce shortcodes</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Compatibility with more themes</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.3 &#8211; Released: Jul 03, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; badge display in widget top related product</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.2 &#8211; Released: Jun 19, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Wrong admin css handle</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.1 &#8211; Released: May 29, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommce 2.3.9</li>\n<li>Update &#8211; Default language file</li>\n<li>Update &#8211; Plugin framework</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Can&#8217;t make a badge issue</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.1.0 &#8211; Released: May 08, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WordPress 4.2.2</li>\n<li>New &#8211; Support to WooCommerce 2.3.8</li>\n<li>Update &#8211; Default language file</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Duplicate product image in shop loop</li>\n<li>Fix &#8211; Minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0 &#8211; Released: Mar 25, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n";s:3:"faq";s:486:"\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Badge Management</code> from Plugins page</li>\n</ol>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Badge Management will add a new submenu called &#8220;Badge Management&#8221; under &#8220;YIT Plugins&#8221; menu. Here you are able t