name";s:32:"YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder";s:4:"slug";s:32:"yith-woocommerce-review-reminder";s:15:"premium_constat";s:12:"YWRR_PREMIUM";s:4:"file";s:8:"init.php";s:7:"wp_info";a:26:{s:4:"name";s:32:"YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder";s:4:"slug";s:32:"yith-woocommerce-review-reminder";s:7:"version";s:5:"1.3.6";s:6:"author";s:43:"<a href="http://yithemes.com/">YITHEMES</a>";s:14:"author_profile";s:39:"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yithemes";s:8:"requires";s:3:"4.0";s:6:"tested";s:5:"4.9.4";s:12:"requires_php";b:0;s:6:"rating";d:66;s:7:"ratings";a:5:{i:5;i:6;i:4;i:1;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:0;i:1;i:5;}s:11:"num_ratings";i:12;s:15:"support_threads";i:5;s:24:"support_threads_resolved";i:1;s:15:"active_installs";i:2000;s:10:"downloaded";i:70050;s:12:"last_updated";s:21:"2018-01-29 4:21pm GMT";s:5:"added";s:10:"2015-02-06";s:8:"homepage";s:67:"http://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder";s:8:"sections";a:5:{s:11:"description";s:1499:"<p>YITH Woocommerce Review Reminder allows you to send, after 7 days the order status is set to &#8220;Completed&#8221;, a reminder to customers with an invitation to make a review of the items purchased.</p>\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Select mail type (HTML or plain text)</li>\n<li>Customize email subject</li>\n<li>Customize email content using a wide set of options</li>\n<li>Use blocklist to add and manage users who do not want to receive further requests.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Full documentation is available <a href="http://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-woocommerce-review-reminder/" rel="nofollow">here</a>.</p>\n<h3>Gợi ý</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder, you can <a href="mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;" title="Your Inspiration Themes" rel="nofollow">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder.</p>\n<h3>Phiên dịch</h3>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tiếng Anh</li>\n<li>Ý</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send <a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Translating_WordPress" title="Translating WordPress" rel="nofollow">gettext PO and MO file</a><br />\n<a href="http://yithemes.com/contact/" title="Your Inspiration Themes" rel="nofollow">use</a> so we can bundle it into YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder languages.</p>\n";s:12:"installation";s:733:"<h4>Installation</h4>\n<p>Important: before of all you have to download and activate WooCommerce plugin, which is mandatory for YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder to be working. If WooCommerce plugin is active, you just need to activate the YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder plugin.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Configuration</h4>\n<p>YITH WooCommerce Review Reminder will add a new tab called &#8220;Review Reminder&#8221; inside the YIT Plugins menu item. There you are able to configure all plugin settings.</p>\n";s:9:"changelog";s:3725:"<h4>Version 1.3.6 &#8211; Released: Jan 29, 2018</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 3.3.0 RC2</li>\n<li>Update: plugin framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.3 &#8211; Released: Sept 20, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: WPML support on unsubscribe link and page</li>\n<li>Update: plugin framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.1 &#8211; Released: May 30, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: review requested when comments are closed</li>\n<li>Update: plugin framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.3.0 &#8211; Released: Mar 16, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Support for WooCommerce 2.7.0-RC 1</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.1 &#8211; Released: Jun 01, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tweak: Support for WooCommerce 2.6.0 beta 3</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.0 &#82