TH Live Chat";s:4:"slug";s:14:"yith-live-chat";s:15:"premium_constat";s:11:"YLC_PREMIUM";s:4:"file";s:8:"init.php";s:7:"wp_info";a:26:{s:4:"name";s:14:"YITH Live Chat";s:4:"slug";s:14:"yith-live-chat";s:7:"version";s:5:"1.2.4";s:6:"author";s:43:"<a href="http://yithemes.com/">YITHEMES</a>";s:14:"author_profile";s:39:"https://profiles.wordpress.org/yithemes";s:8:"requires";s:3:"4.0";s:6:"tested";s:5:"4.9.4";s:12:"requires_php";b:0;s:6:"rating";d:94;s:7:"ratings";a:5:{i:5;i:10;i:4;i:1;i:3;i:0;i:2;i:1;i:1;i:0;}s:11:"num_ratings";i:12;s:15:"support_threads";i:1;s:24:"support_threads_resolved";i:0;s:15:"active_installs";i:2000;s:10:"downloaded";i:67186;s:12:"last_updated";s:22:"2017-12-11 11:43am GMT";s:5:"added";s:10:"2015-03-27";s:8:"homepage";s:50:"http://yithemes.com/themes/plugins/yith-live-chat/";s:8:"sections";a:5:{s:11:"description";s:1488:"<p>Make your client comfortable as in a physical shop</p>\n<p>Users need human contact and YITH Live Chat can help them in overcoming the obstacle of the purchase doubts. Immediate and performing, your users will feel just like they are purchasing in a physical store with this chat. No more time wasted waiting for an answer. A direct contact for a rapid purchase.</p>\n<p>Main features</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Customization of the messages (welcome, greetings, offline, busy operators)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Availability of different tabs, multiple chats</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Full documentation is available <a href="http://yithemes.com/docs-plugins/yith-live-chat/" rel="nofollow">here</a>.</p>\n<h3>Gợi ý</h3>\n<p>If you have suggestions about how to improve YITH Live Chat, you can <a href="mailto:&#112;&#108;&#x75;&#x67;&#x69;&#x6e;&#x73;&#064;&#121;&#105;&#116;&#104;&#x65;&#x6d;&#x65;&#x73;&#x2e;&#099;&#111;&#109;" title="Your Inspiration Themes" rel="nofollow">write us</a> so we can bundle them into YITH Live Chat.</p>\n<h3>Phiên dịch</h3>\n<h4>Available Languages</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Tiếng Anh</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you have created your own language pack, or have an update for an existing one, you can send <a href="https://codex.wordpress.org/Translating_WordPress" title="Translating WordPress" rel="nofollow">gettext PO and MO file</a><br />\n<a href="http://yithemes.com/contact/" title="Your Inspiration Themes" rel="nofollow">use</a> so we can bundle it into YITH Live Chat languages.</p>\n";s:12:"installation";s:517:"<h4>Installation</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH Live Chat</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>cấu hình</h4>\n<p>YITH Live Chat will add a new tab called &#8220;Live Chat&#8221; inside the YIT Plugins menu, where you will be able to configure all plugin settings, and a new menu item called &#8220;YITH Live Chat&#8221;, where there is the chat console.</p>\n";s:9:"changelog";s:2584:"<h4>Version 1.2.4 &#8211; Released: Dec 11, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: plugin framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.3 &#8211; Released: Nov 6, 2017</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: plugin framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.2 &#8211; Released: Nov 7, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: added missing files</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.2.1 &#8211; Released: Oct 12, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: support for CJK characters</li>\n<li>Fix: end conversation issue</li>\n<li>Tweak: Optimized Frontend and Console templates</li>\n<li>Tweak: optimized JS and CSS loading</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.5 &#8211; Released: Apr 20, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: minified version of CSS files</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.4 &#8211; Released: Mar 02, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: hidden on the console page, notifications that disturb the positioning</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.3 &#8211; Released: Feb 09, 2016</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: show offline message if Firebase loses connection</li>\n<li>Fix: chat page lost during page switch</li>\n<li>Fix: notification counter showing incorrect values</li>\n<li>Fix: minor bugs</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.2 &#8211; Released: Oct 30, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: changed text domain from ylc to yith-live-chat</li>\n<li>Update: changed all language file for the new text domain</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.1 &#8211; Released: Oct 29, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Update: plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.1.0 &#8211; Released: Oct 15, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Frontend login username now accepts characters from these Unicode sets: Greek and Coptic, Arabian, Cyrillic, Armenian, Hebrew and Latin-1 (only chars with grave, acute, diaeresis, circumflex, etc.)</li>\n<li>New: minified version of all JS files</li>\n<li>Tweak: Changed global $yith_livechat object to YITH_Live_Chat() singleton.</li>\n<li>Fix: separated JS files for frontend and console</li>\n<li>Fix: code improvements</li>\n<li>Update: language file</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.5 &#8211; Released: Aug 15, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New: Support to WooCommerce 2.4</li>\n<li>Update: Plugin core framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.4 &#8211; Released: July 31, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: session destroy bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.3 &#8211; Released: July 09, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: session destroy bug</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.2 &#8211; Released: May 18, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: code improvements</li>\n<li>Update: language file</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.1 &#8211; Released: May 15, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix: code improvements</li>\n<li>Update: plugin framework</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Version 1.0.0 &#8211; Released: Mar 27, 2015</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release</li>\n</ul>\n";s:3:"faq";s:563:"\n<h4>Installation Instructions</h4>\n<p>\n<h4>Installation</h4>\n<ol>\n<li>Unzip the downloaded zip file.</li>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder into the <code>wp-content/plugins/</code> directory of your WordPress site.</li>\n<li>Activate <code>YITH Live Chat</code> from Plugins page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>cấu hình</h4>\n<p>YITH Live Chat will add a new tab called &#8220;Live Chat&#8221; 